\par 12- "Quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh k\'fb lu\'cbt" l\'b5 quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh b\'bbng v\'a8n b\'b6n c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'f8ng \'ae\'c7u c\'ac quan, t\'e6 ch\'f8c \'ae\'d3 \'b8p d\'f4ng m\'e9t trong c\'b8c h\'d7nh th\'f8c k\'fb lu\'cbt l\'b5 khi\'d3n tr\'b8ch, c
\'b6nh c\'b8o, h\'b9 b\'cbc l\'ad\'acng, h\'b9 ng\'b9ch, c\'b8ch ch\'f8c, bu\'e9c th\'abi vi\'d6c \'ae\'e8i v\'edi c\'b8n b\'e9, c\'abng ch\'f8c thu\'e9c quy\'d2n qu\'b6n l\'fd c\'f1a m\'d7nh theo quy \'ae\'denh c\'f1a ph\'b8p lu\'cbt v\'d2 c\'b8n b\'e9
, c\'abng ch\'f8c. 
\par 13- "Gi\'b6i quy\'d5t khi\'d5u n\'b9i" l\'b5 vi\'d6c x\'b8c minh, k\'d5t lu\'cbn v\'b5 ra quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh gi\'b6i quy\'d5t c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai gi\'b6i quy\'d5t khi\'d5u n\'b9i.
\par 14- "Gi\'b6i quy\'d5t t\'e8 c\'b8o" l\'b5 vi\'d6c x\'b8c minh, k\'d5t lu\'cbn v\'d2 n\'e9i dung t\'e8 c\'b8o v\'b5 vi\'d6c quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh x\'f6 l\'fd c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai gi\'b6i quy\'d5t t\'e8 c\'b8o.
\par 15- "Quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh gi\'b6i quy\'d5t khi\'d5u n\'b9i cu\'e8i c\'efng" l\'b5 quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh c\'e3 hi\'d6u l\'f9c thi h\'b5nh v\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai khi\'d5u n\'b9i kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec quy\'d2n khi\'d5u n\'b9i ti\'d5p.
